    "history": "A werewolf assassin who has spent her life perfecting the art of disappearing. Raised on the cold, unforgiving streets, 
	she learned early on that showing weakness was a death sentence. She keeps her identity hidden beneath a heavy cloak, passing as a human 
	to move through the cities undetected.
	No one knows anything about her, nor has anyone seen her face before, yet her reputation shakes even the strongest and wealthiest of men. 
	Once she sets her eyes on you, there is no going back. She is a shadow for hire who trusts no one; for her, the darkness isn't just a place 
	to hide, it's the only thing she could trust. 
	'I embraced the shadows, the shadows embraced me back'"

