    "name": "The Warden",
    "spriteFile": "res/HeroSprites/Hare.png",
    "history": "A young man, unable to stand the longing for his recently departed beloved, visited her grave under the cover of night.
	 An inhumane shadow lurked behind him. As the sky cleared, revealing some moonlight, he saw it: a hairless, pale mass of human skin 
	 stretched tight over the shape of a rabbit. No fur, no warmth. Only a fixed, glassy stare watching him with patience.
	In a split second, the creature was gone. The only sound left was a swift “thud” coming from a shovel hitting something, followed by 
	the sound of wet stitching in the dark. After some time, the young man was nowhere to be seen, and another rabbit head joined the rows
	 of the silent.
	 'Ah... why is your head like that? Lemme fix it for you.'"
